- date: 2026-05-14
  kind: brand
  old: orionfoldllc
  new: Orionfold
  affected: [prose_mentions, hf_repo_urls, frontmatter.product, model_card_attribution]
  status: complete
  swept_at: 2026-05-14
  swept_by: manavsehgal/ainative-business.github.io@85f9307
  notes: |
    HF publishing surface moved from fallback org `orionfoldllc` (registered
    2026-05-13 when the short slug `orionfold` was unavailable) to the existing
    personal user handle `Orionfold` — Bartowski-precedent. fieldkit constant
    ORIONFOLD_HF_ORG → ORIONFOLD_HF_HANDLE (old name kept as back-compat alias).
    The LLC parent brand survives off-HF (legal entity, billing, footer
    attribution); the HF surface is the user. Mac side: replay across
    destination prose + tag pages + model-card attribution.
    Mac sweep 2026-05-14: zero destination footprint to rewrite — the incoming
    article (becoming-a-gguf-publisher-on-spark) already shipped with the new
    name in frontmatter, tags, and HF repo URLs. Status flipped to complete.
